            "title": "即月期指開報24085點 低水146點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報24085點，跌153點，較上日現貨收市價24231點低水146點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報6000點，跌37點，低水37點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8866點，跌50點，低水48點。</p>\n</div>",
